description:
So I (think I) have fixed the corrupt file and made general notation improvements here and there. I also cleaned up the track names and added clean guitars and more keyboard tracks as nessecary. Because of that I needed to merge two of the vocals tracks together so Songsterr can play every track. 

I also moved most of the guitar parts into the tracks labelled "8-String", with separate solo tracks for when the higher strings are used. This may make learning the song a little annoying, but I can't think of any other resolution for 8-string guitars.
title: Cockroach King
